---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About — Stop Think Pivot"
  description="What Stop Think Pivot is about and who's behind it."
>
  <div style="padding: 4rem 0 6rem;">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="about-section">
        <h1>About</h1>

        <p>
          Life has a way of carrying you somewhere you never chose to go.
          Not because you're weak — but because you never stopped long enough
          to ask where you were headed.
        </p>

        <p>
          <strong>Stop Think Pivot</strong> is where I work through the stuff that matters.
          Faith. Business. The gap between who you are and who you're becoming.
          Lessons learned the hard way, shared without polish.
        </p>

        <blockquote>
          Don't let life push you around. Stop. Think. Pivot.
        </blockquote>

        <p>
          The name is a sequence. And it only works if you actually do the first one.
          Most people skip straight to the pivot — reacting, rerouting, spinning — without
          ever standing still long enough to understand why they need to change course.
        </p>

        <p>
          That's what this is for.
        </p>

        <div class="ember-divider">&#9679;</div>

        <p style="color: var(--text-muted); font-size: 0.9rem;">
          If something here hits close to home, reach out.
          I'm not hard to find.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
